{"ts": "2026-06-07T22:28:09.990039+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The repository **requires contributors to use `pnpm`** and **npm is explicitly not acceptable**. Two clear pieces of evidence in `package.json` justify this:\n\n1. **`\"preinstall\": \"npx only-allow pnpm\"`** — This script runs before every install. `only-allow` checks which package manager is being used and will **abort the install with an error** if anything other than `pnpm` is detected. This is the primary guardrail: running `npm install` would trigger this hook and fail immediately.\n\n2. **`\"packageManager\": \"pnpm@10.20.0\"`** — This field (from the [Corepack](https://nodejs.org/api/core.html#corepack) / `packageManager` convention) declares the project's pinned package manager and version. Tools that honor it (Corepack, `only-allow`, CI pipelines, etc.) will expect and enforce pnpm 10.20.0.\n\n**In short:** anyone who tries `npm install` will be blocked at the `preinstall` hook. `pnpm` is the sole supported package manager for this repository.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 319, "prompt_tokens": 4836, "total_tokens": 5155, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 74, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 4160, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.000195608, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.000106288, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 8.932e-05}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780871285-kxM0vjDkoF7xvXgXABiE", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea433-4a37-7243-a3b5-bd64addc9d03-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_c